title: GTA.IV.SAVEGAME[100%]-OSKARTiST
description:
Instructions:
1. Put the contents of the folder "wrapper" in the GTA IV game directory.
2. Launch "CopyXLiveResources.exe" and click Yes.
3. Copy the contents of the folder save to "C:UsersXXXAppDataLocalRockstar GamesGTA IVsavegamesuser_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"
4. Launch the game and enjoy.
PLEASE NOTE: THE SAVE DIRECTORY IS VISTA ONLY, IF IT DOES NOT EXIST ON WINXP, Google is your friend.
